---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Legal Notice | Ads Calculator';
const description = 'Legal Notice and Terms of Use for Ads Calculator. Operator identification, user conditions, intellectual property details, and liability disclaimers.';
const keywords = 'legal notice, terms of use, ads calculator legal, operator info, disclaimer';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} keywords={keywords} lang="en">
  <main class="flex-grow py-12 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl border border-white/20 dark:border-white/5 p-8 sm:p-12 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-1000">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2 tracking-tight">Legal Notice</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Website Owner & Operator Information</h2>
          <p>In accordance with information society services regulations, users are informed that this website, <strong>adsroicalc.com</strong> (hereinafter referred to as the "Site"), is owned and operated by <strong>PauApps</strong>.</p>
          <p>For inquiries, questions, or formal contact, users can reach us at our main administrative email: <a href="mailto:info@adsroicalc.com" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">info@adsroicalc.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. Purpose of the Site</h2>
          <p>The Site serves exclusively as a digital platform offering calculation tools tailored to advertising, business ROI, and growth marketing metrics. The calculators, charts, and associated features are designed to help digital marketers analyze campaigns, breakeven thresholds, and overall advertisement profit indicators.</p>
          <p>Accessing the Site is free, voluntary, and implies immediate agreement with the terms and disclaimers detailed herein.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Disclaimer of Liability</h2>
          <p>The calculations and simulations provided by the tools on this Site are for <strong>informational, illustrative, and educational purposes only</strong>. The values and results are estimates based on user-inputted numbers and do not guarantee actual business performance or tax/financial exactitude.</p>
          <p>Consequently, the operator of the Site shall not be held liable for:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Decisions or actions taken by users or third parties based on the results generated by the Site's calculators.</li>
            <li>Any financial or marketing losses, budget overruns, or operational failures arising from the use of the calculators.</li>
            <li>Errors, inaccuracies, or programmatic bugs that might occur during client-side calculations or chart rendering.</li>
            <li>Temporary technical issues, downtime, or lack of availability of the Site.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Intellectual and Industrial Property</h2>
          <p>All content, branding, design code, icons, logos, graphic design layouts, scripts, text documentation, and calculation logic displayed on the Site are the exclusive intellectual property of the operator (PauApps) or its licensed providers, protected by national and international copyright laws.</p>
          <p>Any reproduction, distribution, public transmission, transformation, or exploitation of the code or content of this Site without the express prior written consent of the owner is strictly prohibited.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Rules of Use</h2>
          <p>Users agree to use the Site in accordance with the law, decency, public order, and these conditions. Users will refrain from using the Site for illicit purposes, or in any way that damages, disables, overburdens, or prevents the normal operation of the service for other users.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">6. External Links & Advertisements</h2>
          <p>The Site contains advertisements served by Google AdSense and may contain links to third-party portals or resources. The operator has no control over these external sites, does not endorse them, and accepts no liability for their contents, terms, or privacy policies. Accessing external links is done solely at the user's own risk.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">7. Jurisdiction and Applicable Law</h2>
          <p>This Legal Notice and the relations between the user and the operator shall be governed by Spanish law. For any conflict or dispute arising from the interpretation or breach of these terms, both parties submit to the jurisdiction of the competent courts of the operator's domicile, unless otherwise mandated by consumer protection regulations.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
